OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with late sunny spells leading
OL,7,Fto clear spells after sunset.
OL,8,FOvernight remaining dry with long
OL,9,Fclear spells for most, but turning
OL,10,Fcloudier in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FSunny spells to start inland
OL,13,Fbut soon turning cloudy through the
OL,14,Fmorning. Rain affecting coastal areas
OL,15,Fat first, then spreading eastwards
OL,16,Fthrough the afternoon and turning
OL,17,Fheavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
